<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَانْظُرْ مُصْطَلَحَ:</span> <span class="c2">(نَقْش)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧ - هَذَا وَتَجُوزُ الزَّخْرَفَةُ بِغَيْرِ الذَّهَبِ وَالْفِضَّةِ فِي الأَْقْمِشَةِ وَالْخَشَبِ وَغَيْرِ ذَلِكَ وَسَائِرِ الأَْمْتِعَةِ مَا لَمْ يَصِل إِلَى دَرَجَةِ الإِْسْرَافِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>زَرَافَة<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
